The paper involves the use of neural style transfer, which is a popular technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for image stylization. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks and loss functions, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the generation of fonts, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
